data.description: DAYLIGHT BASEMENT! Beautifully Updated and Spacious 2488SF. 3 BDRM upstairs plus two more additional rooms with closets downstairs. Convenient for multi-generational living. Gorgeous kitchen; Granite countertops, newer stainless steel appliances incl. a double oven. Dining room w/ french doors leading to the expansive deck w/Catio. Primary Suite on main level w/ walk-in closet and built-in shelving. Downstairs you will find 2 add'l rooms w/closets, a family room w/freestanding gas stove, large flex space & storage room. New roof, gutters, garage doors, interior & exterior paint, and More! Large .20 acre lot. Mature landscaping, water feature, fenced backyard that backs up to green space for extra privacy.
